Configuring Nette
*****************

.[perex]
An overview of all configuration options in the Nette Framework.

Nette components are configured using configuration files, which are usually written in the [NEON format|neon:format]. They are best edited in [editors that support it |best-practices:editors-and-tools#IDE Editor]. If you are using the full framework, the configuration will be [loaded during application boot |application:bootstrap#DI Container Configuration]; if not, read [how to load the configuration|bootstrap:].

